{"name":"Chloé Zhao","photo":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ac/Chlo%C3%A9_Zhao_at_the_2026_Berlin_International_Film_Festival-68507.jpg/250px-Chlo%C3%A9_Zhao_at_the_2026_Berlin_International_Film_Festival-68507.jpg","bio":null,"films":[{"id":"wjdlGiN-GFI2","title":"Hamnet","year":"2025","stars":null,"genres":["Drama","Romantiek"],"description":"Historisch drama over Agnes en Shakespeare's rouw na Hamnets dood.","synopsis":"Dit historische drama, geregisseerd door Chloé Zhao en gebaseerd op de roman van Maggie O'Farrell, verbeeldt het leven van Agnes (Jessie Buckley) en haar echtgenoot William Shakespeare (Paul Mescal) in het 16e-eeuwse Engeland. Het verhaal volgt hun ontmoeting, hun huwelijk en de tragische dood van hun 11-jarige zoon Hamnet aan de pest. De film toont hoe dit immense verlies en de daaropvolgende rouw de relatie tussen de ouders beïnvloedt en uiteindelijk de inspiratie vormt voor Shakespeare's meesterwerk *Hamlet*.","awards":[{"ceremony":"Golden Globe","year":"2026","status":"win","category":"Beste film (drama)","categoryKey":"best picture drama","entityType":"film","name":"Hamnet (2025)🌈🌈🌈🌈"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2026","status":"nomination","category":"Beste film (drama)","categoryKey":"best picture drama","entityType":"film","name":"Hamnet (2025)🌈🌈🌈🌈"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2026","status":"nomination","category":"Bewerkt scenario","categoryKey":"adapted screenplay","entityType":"film","name":"Hamnet (2025)🌈🌈🌈🌈"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2026","status":"nomination","category":"Kostuumontwerp","categoryKey":"costume design","entityType":"film","name":"Hamnet (2025)🌈🌈🌈🌈"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2026","status":"nomination","category":"Productieontwerp","categoryKey":"production design","entityType":"film","name":"Hamnet (2025)🌈🌈🌈🌈"},{"ceremony":"Critics choice","year":"2026","status":"nomination","category":"Beste film (drama)","categoryKey":"best picture drama","entityType":"film","name